{
  "name": "RPlog_Leia_s_Advice",
  "title": "Leia's Advice",
  "summary": "Shaken by a report on her carbonite-rescued cousin Sabrina, Minister Leia Organa Solo summons her brother Luke Skywalker to her Senate office on Coruscant. Luke confirms that Sabrina survived the Nar Shaddaa mission but senses a darkness in her, fearing the Sith Lord Vadim reached her first, and the twins resolve to help her together. Talk turns to Johanna's looming Senate hearing, and Luke worries that defending her may force them to reveal the secret of the resurrected Emperor, risking a violent backlash. After the Quarren Barrien Thrask briefly interrupts with news of Karrde, Luke guides Leia through a profound Force-meditation that unifies their spirits in harmony for hours. Renewed and reassured, they close by planning a dinner to discuss reassigning the Firecat pilots Enb'Zik and Snarl.",
